  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Cut the tofu into 1-inch cubes.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the olive oil, paprika, salt, pepper, and lemon juice.",
    "Add the tofu cubes to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Thread the marinated tofu onto the skewers.",
    "Brush the grill with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
